<GUIClass name="GTE_OperatorPinCheck" id="644f7002-f2d0-4d6d-94d3-1b5d83fe3820">
    <superclass name="CMUI_Modal"/>
    <transient/>
    <subclassTransientAllowed/>
    <transientAllowed/>
    <text>cnwrd1 CCMS POL 2032 par 25594 10.12.2010

Use to gather operator pin numbers for new cargo when required.

when terminal edi option 'EDI Operator Stop Process Release PIN' is on
When the operator for the release requires pin verification</text>
